text: Kalabagan () is a Thana in Dhaka, Bangladesh, adjacent to Dhanmondi and Jatiya Sangsad. == Geography == Kalabagan has an area of 1.26 km2. == Demographics == According to the 2001 Bangladesh census there are about 106671 people living in Kalabagan. == Establishments == * Kalabagan Cricket Academy * Kala Bagan Krira Chakra == References == Category:Thanas of Dhaka Category:Dhaka Division geography stubs
